        }
    }

This way, you enable Spring to proxy it with AOP when intercepting it in an `@Aspect`, by putting your `JdbcTemplate` bean into `ApplicationContext`. You can now autowire it with:

    @Autowired private JdbcTemplate jdbcTemplate;

